com.igeekinc.util.fileinfo

Class FileClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.igeekinc.util.fileinfo.TreeInfoBase
      • com.igeekinc.util.fileinfo.FileClass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FileClass
extends TreeInfoBase
implements java.io.Serializable
    FileClass defines a class of file. FileClass has a hierarchy of types. All file classes need to descend from the kRootClass. New top level classes can be defined as necessary.
    See Also:
